The staff were friendly and very helpful.	We had a room on the 4th floor which was nice and spotlessly clean.	The room was modern and clean.	The room was adequate in size and very quiet with a good, clean bathroom.	Rooms are clean and comfortable.	The receptionist when we arrived was very friendly and helpful.	The room was lovely and clean and spacious with a view of the eiffel tower in the distance.	The location of the hotel is great.	The rooms were clean, and the bathrooms were very nice.